      "message": "Patch Set 8: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nAs previously reviewed for change #3, the version check for 2.4.99 is too late in the development cycle to catch this if there is a problem. It should be 2.4.55 or only a little later in the development cycle to implement the proper rename locking.\n\nBy 2.4.99 we would already be into RC1, so that would be too late to notice that something still needs to be fixed.",
